      "description": "Timeout in milliseconds for MCP tool execution (default: 100000000, about 28 hours). A per-server `timeout` field in `.mcp.json` overrides this for that server. A per-server `timeout` of at least 1000 also sets the minimum idle window for that server's tool calls, so `CLAUDE_CODE_MCP_TOOL_IDLE_TIMEOUT` never aborts them sooner; this floor requires Claude Code v2.1.203 or later. For the env variable, values below 1000 are floored to one second; for the per-server field, values below 1000 are ignored",
